After you [enable dual authorization for an instance](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/hs-crypto?topic=hs-crypto-manage-dual-auth) or [for a key](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/hs-crypto?topic=hs-crypto-set-dual-auth-key-policy), you can provide the first authorization to delete a key by using the IBM Cloud console.



